WEBVTT

00:00.078 --> 00:01.708
Previously on "Cloak & Dagger"...

00:01.738 --> 00:04.308
Given that you murdered
my firstborn in cold blood,

00:04.338 --> 00:06.578
we'll see if your value to Tyrone

00:06.608 --> 00:08.900
outweighs the need for
me to end your life.

00:08.925 --> 00:11.648
Leaving someone who
hurts you isn't hard, Mom.

00:11.678 --> 00:12.823
You just leave.

00:13.112 --> 00:15.418
In the dociles, there's
almost no activity

00:15.458 --> 00:17.494
in the anger and rage center
of the cerebral cortex.

00:17.518 --> 00:20.388
But in the aggressives, it's
as if there's nothing but...

00:20.428 --> 00:22.038
- Mayhem.
- That's what you do, right?

00:22.063 --> 00:24.434
You get inside people's
minds, and you cause them pain?

00:24.458 --> 00:26.698
If you can't be merciful
when you play God,

00:26.728 --> 00:29.290
what kind of God will you be
when you ain't playing no more?

00:29.315 --> 00:30.428
Why don't we find out?

00:30.468 --> 00:32.993
You and Tandy live in different worlds.

00:36.508 --> 00:37.578
Tandy!

00:44.408 --> 00:45.538
Ty?

00:46.137 --> 00:47.267
Ty!

00:47.748 --> 00:48.988
Hey, look at me.

00:49.501 --> 00:50.701
Look at me, Ty.

