Ty?

01:48.213 --> 01:49.326
Hey!

01:49.351 --> 01:50.481
Hey, Ty, look at me.

01:52.330 --> 01:54.130
Tyrone! Come on, Tyrone!

01:55.260 --> 01:56.460
Ty!

